  "description": "## Deep Component Audit ‚Äî hx-field\n\n**Component directory:** `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-field/`\n**wc-mcp Health Score:** 88 (B)\n**Known issues:** _hasLabelSlot, _hasErrorSlot, _hasHelpSlot, _fieldId, _helpTextId, _errorId ‚Äî all missing descriptions.\n\n### wc-mcp Tools ‚Äî USE THESE FOR SCORING\n- `score_component`, `get_component`, `analyze_accessibility`, `validate_usage`, `list_css_parts`, `list_events`, `list_slots`, `get_design_tokens`\n- **Report any wc-mcp bugs to `/Volumes/Development/booked/wc-tools` board.**\n\n### Audit Scope\n1. **Design Tokens** ‚Äî `--hx-` tokens. Label, help text, error text colors/spacing. Dark mode.\n2. **Accessibility** ‚Äî WCAG 2.1 AA. Label association (for/id). Required indicator. Error association (aria-describedby). Help text association.\n3. **Functionality** ‚Äî Label/help-text/error-text slots. Required indicator. Slot presence detection. ID generation for ARIA associations.\n4. **TypeScript** ‚Äî Strict. No `any`. Proper ID management.\n5. **CSS/Styling** ‚Äî Shadow DOM. CSS Parts. Layout (label above, beside). Spacing.\n6. **CEM Accuracy** ‚Äî Fix all 6 missing descriptions.\n7. **Tests** ‚Äî 80%+ coverage. Slots. ARIA associations. Required. Error state.\n8. **Storybook** ‚Äî With/without label. Help text. Error. Required.\n9. **Drupal Compatibility** ‚Äî Form element wrapper. Twig-friendly.\n10. **Portability** ‚Äî CDN-ready.\n\n### Deliverable\nDetailed audit report. Fix CRITICAL+HIGH. Document rest.",
